cs.CR, cs.SE, cs.DS, cs.DB, cs.PL

Reasoning: 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on privacy and sensitive information leakage in mobile applications. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is also likely as the paper proposes a system to detect sensitive information leakage in Android applications. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.DB (Databases) are possible categories as the paper uses a clustering method to generate signatures and analyze network traffic. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is also a possible category as the paper discusses the behavior of applications and their use of advertisement modules.
